reviewText: I THOUGHT THIS WAS A GUIDE TO BECOMING INDEPENDENT. NO. IT IS ANBOUT A LOSER AND ANOTHER ONE AND ALL THAT GOES FROM THEM TO METH

The previous reviewer says it all, I will only add that this may be the only chance you have to see the best of the Westmores (the great makeup artist dynasty) apply a full face of makeup. You've never seen so much powder!
